data.description: New!!! Extra - limited time offer $2,000 Realtor bonus with accepted contract. Welcome to this charming and well-maintained four-sided brick exterior home located in the heart of NW San Antonio. This lovely home shows pride of home ownership. Freshly painted through-out and Ready for quick Move-in! Two story home comprised of four bedrooms with two and a half baths. A massive island stands out in the kitchen along with breakfast sit-in area. Ceramic tile on 1st floor, wood stair treads, tile & carpet upstairs. Installed water softener, storm doors, ceiling fans and 2 in faux wood blinds. The master bathroom comes with popular separate his and her vanities, along with separate walk-in closets! Make your way outside onto the spacious covered deck that opens to a backyard with plenty of room to entertain including a hot tub. Seller is offering $2,000 carpet allowance. Be the first to view before it goes. Schedule your private showing today.
